## 4. Payments & Operations

- **Preferred:** Bitcoin + Lightning only (or heavy preference).
- No Visa/Mastercard if possible. No custodial intermediaries.
- No-account, no-tracking shopping model.
- Offer offline/mail-in sats options for maximum privacy.
- Lightning invoices + on-chain fallbacks.
- Print-and-pay QR codes for in-person or mailed orders.

**Goal:** Every transaction reinforces the parallel economy.

