## 5. Guerrilla Commerce Tactics (Amazon Counter-Attack)

- Aggressively price key physical titles below Amazon where margins allow.
- Monitor and acquire high-quality physical overstock as Amazon pushes digital.
- Create inventory arbitrage loops: sats → physical inventory → more sats.
- Emphasize “physical media preservation” in all messaging.
- Position as the analog resistance layer while others go full digital.

